# Cloudflare Pages Redirects
# Primary Domain: coastlinesprayfoam.com
# Secondary Domain: coastlinesprayfoamsolutions.com (redirects to primary)

# Redirect secondary domain to primary domain (all variations)
https://coastlinesprayfoamsolutions.com/* https://coastlinesprayfoam.com/:splat 301!
https://www.coastlinesprayfoamsolutions.com/* https://coastlinesprayfoam.com/:splat 301!
http://coastlinesprayfoamsolutions.com/* https://coastlinesprayfoam.com/:splat 301!
http://www.coastlinesprayfoamsolutions.com/* https://coastlinesprayfoam.com/:splat 301!

# Redirect www to non-www for primary domain
https://www.coastlinesprayfoam.com/* https://coastlinesprayfoam.com/:splat 301!

# Force HTTPS for primary domain
http://coastlinesprayfoam.com/* https://coastlinesprayfoam.com/:splat 301!
http://www.coastlinesprayfoam.com/* https://coastlinesprayfoam.com/:splat 301!

# Internal page redirects
/home / 301
/index.html / 301
